# Database Connection
# =====================

# Local development (SQLite) - Copy this to .env for local dev
DATABASE_URL="file:./dev.db"

# Production (PostgreSQL) - Use one of these options:

# Option 1: Vercel Postgres (recommended)
# Vercel auto-injects these variables, just reference them:
# DATABASE_URL="${POSTGRES_PRISMA_URL}"

# Option 2: External PostgreSQL (Supabase, Neon, Railway, etc.)
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@host:5432/database?schema=public"

# Option 3: Local PostgreSQL (if you prefer Postgres locally too)
# DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres:password@localhost:5432/lifeboard"

# =====================
# IMPORTANT: Update prisma/schema.prisma provider when switching:
# - SQLite: provider = "sqlite"
# - PostgreSQL: provider = "postgresql"
# =====================
